### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/sales/api
@brandId = 1
@subcategoryId = 1
@productId = 1

### ==========================================
### SEARCH — RUTAS PÚBLICAS (sin token)
### ==========================================

### Search by brand (válido ✅)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/brand/{{brandId}} HTTP/1.1

### ==========================================

### Search by subcategory (válido ✅)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/subcategory/{{subcategoryId}} HTTP/1.1

### ==========================================

### Search by product (válido ✅)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/product/{{productId}} HTTP/1.1

### ==========================================

### Get subcategories with specs (válido ✅)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/subcategories HTTP/1.1

### ==========================================

### Search brand (no existe — 204 sin contenido)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/brand/999 HTTP/1.1

### ==========================================

### Search subcategory (no existe — 204 sin contenido)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/subcategory/999 HTTP/1.1

### ==========================================

### Search product (no existe — 204 sin contenido)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/product/999 HTTP/1.1

### ==========================================

### Search brand (id inválido — 422 ❌)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/brand/abc HTTP/1.1

### ==========================================

### Search subcategory (id inválido — 422 ❌)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/subcategory/abc HTTP/1.1

### ==========================================

### Search product (id inválido — 422 ❌)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/product/abc HTTP/1.1